# ============================================================================
# USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.sepolia .env
#
# 2. Update BLOCKCHAIN_RPC_URL with your Infura or Alchemy API key
#
# 3. Update WALLET_ADDRESS with your agent's wallet address
#
# 4. Get Sepolia testnet ETH from faucet:
#    - https://sepoliafaucet.com
#    - https://www.alchemy.com/faucets/ethereum-sepolia
#
# 5. Run the agent:
#    ./payment-agent
#
